attributes.Long form description: The student is inspecting and repairing a piece of furniture. The student grabs a wrench and begin to unscrew the wheels of the furniture. The student then rotates the shelf and begin to disassemble the wheels. The student then unscrews the trays and disassembles them. The student then unscrew and disassemble the legs of the shelf before finally disassembling the base.

attributes.Transcription: Alright. So now please disassemble this shelf.

attributes.Action sentence: The student inspects the furniture regularly.
